{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/WorkflowModals\/documentation\/WorkflowModals\/ModalContainer"},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"Use a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ModalContainer"},{"text":" to render a base screen and an array of modals on top of it.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ModalContainer","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"BaseContent","kind":"genericParameter"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ModalContent","kind":"genericParameter"},{"text":">","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"overview","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When modals are added or removed from a container, the screen will animate the changes based on","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the modals keys. If new modals are added, a presentation animation will occur, and if modals are","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"removed, a dismissal animation will occur. Existing modals will have their screens updated.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This container uses the modal system to trampoline modals to a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"x-source-tag:\/\/ModalHost"},{"type":"text","text":", which must be installed somewhere in your hierarchy."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"In a pure workflow application, you should install a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"x-source-tag:\/\/ModalHostContainer"},{"type":"text","text":" at the root of your app."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"In a hybrid application, you should install a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"x-source-tag:\/\/ModalHostContainerViewController"},{"type":"text","text":" instead,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in which case you do not need to use a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ModalHostContainer"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Note that modals are updated asynchronously, so this container won’t present or dismiss modals","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"synchronously during the screen update of a workflow render.","type":"text"}]}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/workflowmodals\/modalcontainer"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"ModalContainer","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"s:14WorkflowModals14ModalContainerV","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ModalContainer","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Structure","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"WorkflowModals"}],"title":"ModalContainer","symbolKind":"struct"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WorkflowModals\/documentation\/WorkflowModals"]]},"relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/WorkflowModals\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/WorkflowModals\/10WorkflowUI6ScreenP","doc:\/\/WorkflowModals\/10WorkflowUI22SingleScreenContainingP"],"kind":"relationships","type":"conformsTo","title":"Conforms To"}],"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/WorkflowModals\/documentation\/WorkflowModals\/ModalContainer\/init(base:modals:)-8z69p","doc:\/\/WorkflowModals\/documentation\/WorkflowModals\/ModalContainer\/init(base:modals:)-9lnh9"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers","title":"Initializers"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/WorkflowModals\/documentation\/WorkflowModals\/ModalContainer\/base","doc:\/\/WorkflowModals\/documentation\/WorkflowModals\/ModalContainer\/modals"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties","title":"Instance Prop